README: contains all of the information in this file

Makefile: make contains dist, default, clean, check, dist 

lab4b.c: C source code for program that polls for the temperature from a Grove Cape that
is connected to a button and a temperature sensor. Periodically receives commands and 
periodically provides time and temperature information.

smoketest.sh: Smoke Test script that is run by make check to make sure the program has initialized the sensors and is running properly.


References:
http://wiki.seeedstudio.com/Grove-Temperature_Sensor_V1.2/
https://iotdk.intel.com/docs/master/mraa/
http://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man2/poll.2.html
